{"tid":1822114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[119大遊行]大家成日話行動post推唔到上熱門 我有辦法","createTime":"2020-01-12T17:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T09:27:15.000Z","uid":26876,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"210dded73fec7a1f1b8e82b9da8faadd8741ff7f","tid":1822114,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"就係無論開乜Post都好 <br />\n<br />\n就係唔理你開乜嘢Post都<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">喺標題前面到加上最近行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁咪成版都係行動文宣囉<br />\n<br />\n如果無行動都加句口號 喺標題前面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n［光復香港時代革命］xxxxxx<br />\n[五大訴求缺一不可]xxxxxxxx<br />\n[黑警死全家]xxxxxxx<br />\n<br />\n[支持黃色經濟]xxxxxxx<br />\n<br />\n［罷良元氣] xxxxxxx"},{"pid":"cdaf2098010e49ef54844e84254543d5f6a43c58","tid":1822114,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"點解你啲例如唔係行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a508a6e095d957ce98e7dd5471149ca847e991f","tid":1822114,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdaf2098010e49ef54844e84254543d5f6a43c58","tid":1822114,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:44:47.000Z","msg":"點解你啲例如唔係行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:45:39.000Z","msg":"講緊無行動果陣最少都加行動喺前面"},{"pid":"6b3828169fe7a06f11869152b2f0c720560d4cfd","tid":1822114,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhhhhh<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n警暴製亂<br />\n支暴製亂</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0Ezf7k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0Ezf7k.jpg&h=0e61caff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗隊特突比你捉到鬼，反正比你捉到隻鬼又唔會有咩後果，仲可以引大家捉鬼，透過捉鬼內部分化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n沒有普選 唯有獨立</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ytpdxK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ytpdxK.jpg&h=cebe6b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">荷包在我手 藍店抖一抖</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">抵制藍店 支持黃色經濟圈</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u603t5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu603t5D.jpg&h=0f9c2c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府正用盡一切手段迫企業歸邊，為示威者樹敵，為求社會各界與抗爭人士割蓆<br />\n<br />\n黑警透過非法濫捕，圖阻嚇港人表達訴求，損害香港言論、集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6wEt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6wEt9.jpg&h=75dfc14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avbtvJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavbtvJ0.jpg&h=e1c98503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hppS6Sz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhppS6Sz.jpg&h=867a6106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n齊心祝福<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ug7anh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fug7anh2.png&h=2bf968e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3726665f7ebcb022153513dc3791a0d4166ed57f","tid":1822114,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a30024c363f33615b38fd1551ca8b4fbaa264dc","tid":1822114,"uid":21